! version = 2.0

// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
//  Assistant — default persona
//
//  Simple, human, casual. Not a business bot.
//  Shows a persona catalog when asked for help.
// ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

! local concat = newline

// ── Persona Identity ─────────────────────────────────────────
! var name    = Assistant
! var persona = assistant

// ── Main Topic (includes shared conversation) ────────────────
> topic random includes conversation jwlinker

  // ── Help / Persona Catalog ─────────────────────────────────
  + (help|ede|èd|menu)
  * <get lang> == en => Here's what I can do:
  ^ \n
  ^ \n💬 *Chat* — just talk to me naturally
  ^ \n🛒 *talk to sales* — plans, pricing, promos
  ^ \n🔧 *talk to support* — tech help, tickets
  ^ \n📖 *talk to talkprep* — sermon prep coach
  ^ \n
  ^ \nOr just ask me anything 👇
  - Men sa m ka fè pou ou:
  ^ \n
  ^ \n💬 *Chat* — jis pale avè m nòmalman
  ^ \n🛒 *pale ak vant* — plan, pri, pwomosyon
  ^ \n🔧 *pale ak support* — èd teknik, tiket
  ^ \n📖 *pale ak talkprep* — coaching prèch
  ^ \n
  ^ \nOswa jis poze m kesyon w 👇

  // ── Who are you ────────────────────────────────────────────
  + (who are you|ki moun ou ye|kiles ou ye|what are you)
  * <get lang> == en => I'm your assistant 😊 I can chat, answer questions, or connect you with a specialist. Type *help* to see what's available.
  - Mwen se asistan w 😊 Mwen ka pale, reponn kesyon, oswa konekte w ak yon espesyalis. Tape *ede* pou wè sa ki disponib.

  // ── Acknowledgments — stay silent ──────────────────────────
  + (ok|okay|ok sa|oke|alright|aight|gotcha|bet|cool|nice|lol|haha|mdrrr)
  - {{silent}}

  + (wi|yes|yeah|yep)
  - {{silent}}

  + (no|nah|nope)
  - {{silent}}

  // ── AI Fallback ────────────────────────────────────────────
  + *
  - {{ai_fallback}}

< topic
